  <section>
    <h2>Accessibility</h2>
    <p>Screen readers typically do not announce <code>&lt;var&gt;</code> differently from surrounding text. The accent color provides a visual cue only. For mathematical expressions where variables are critical to understanding, consider using <a href="/docs/elements/native/math/"><code>&lt;math&gt;</code></a> (MathML) for richer semantics.</p>
  </section>

